{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":587,"text":"Humanity takes center stage at TED,"},{"time":3650,"text":"but I would like to add \na voice for the animals,"},{"time":7313,"text":"whose bodies and minds \nand spirits shaped us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13112,"text":"Some years ago, it was my good fortune"},{"time":16358,"text":"to meet a tribal elder on an island"},{"time":18306,"text":"not far from Vancouver."},{"time":20860,"text":"His name is Jimmy Smith,"},{"time":23238,"text":"and he shared a story with me"},{"time":25487,"text":"that is told among his people,"},{"time":27840,"text":"who call themselves the Kwikwasut'inuxw."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31035,"text":"Once upon a time, he told me,"},{"time":33730,"text":"all animals on Earth were one."},{"time":36587,"text":"Even though they look different on the outside,"},{"time":39511,"text":"inside, they're all the same,"},{"time":42751,"text":"and from time to time they would gather"},{"time":45406,"text":"at a sacred cave deep inside the forest"},{"time":48156,"text":"to celebrate their unity."},{"time":50648,"text":"When they arrived,"},{"time":52392,"text":"they would all take off their skins."},{"time":54920,"text":"Raven shed his feathers, bear his fur,"},{"time":58444,"text":"and salmon her scales,"},{"time":60907,"text":"and then, they would dance."},{"time":63829,"text":"But one day, a human made it to the cave"},{"time":67130,"text":"and laughed at what he saw"},{"time":68714,"text":"because he did not understand."},{"time":71838,"text":"Embarrassed, the animals fled,"},{"time":74707,"text":"and that was the last time"},{"time":76934,"text":"they revealed themselves this way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80556,"text":"The ancient understanding that underneath"},{"time":83240,"text":"their separate identities, all animals are one,"},{"time":86143,"text":"has been a powerful inspiration to me."},{"time":89881,"text":"I like to get past the fur, the feathers"},{"time":92944,"text":"and the scales."},{"time":94573,"text":"I want to get under the skin."},{"time":96801,"text":"No matter whether I'm facing a giant elephant"},{"time":99601,"text":"or a tiny tree frog,"},{"time":101749,"text":"my goal is to connect us with them, eye to eye."}]},{"cues":[{"time":108641,"text":"You may wonder, do I ever photograph people?"},{"time":111780,"text":"Sure. People are always present in my photos,"},{"time":115615,"text":"no matter whether they appear"},{"time":117742,"text":"to portray tortoises"},{"time":120561,"text":"or cougars"},{"time":122374,"text":"or lions."},{"time":124253,"text":"You just have to learn how \nto look past their disguise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128751,"text":"As a photographer,"},{"time":130485,"text":"I try to reach beyond the differences"},{"time":133300,"text":"in our genetic makeup"},{"time":135264,"text":"to appreciate all we have in common"},{"time":138861,"text":"with every other living thing."},{"time":142239,"text":"When I use my camera,"},{"time":144568,"text":"I drop my skin"},{"time":146491,"text":"like the animals at that cave"},{"time":149191,"text":"so I can show who they really are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153128,"text":"As animals blessed"},{"time":155378,"text":"with the power of rational thought,"},{"time":158752,"text":"we can marvel at the intricacies of life."},{"time":163285,"text":"As citizens of a planet in trouble,"},{"time":166121,"text":"it is our moral responsibility"},{"time":168685,"text":"to deal with the dramatic loss in diversity of life."},{"time":174240,"text":"But as humans with hearts,"},{"time":176107,"text":"we can all rejoice in the unity of life,"},{"time":180040,"text":"and perhaps we can change"},{"time":182880,"text":"what once happened in that sacred cave."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186760,"text":"Let's find a way to join the dance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191992,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194775,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}